[SN]TITLE[SN]
Pair held in Aberdeen over £22,000 cocaine haul

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man and woman have been detained after cocaine with an estimated street value of about £22,000 was recovered in Aberdeen.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police Scotland said it followed an intelligence-led operation in the Rockall Place area on Wednesday.
A man aged 24 and woman aged 28 were held.
They are expected to appear at Aberdeen Sheriff Court.
